 {"id":"brenner_bot-kpso","title":"Landing Page: Tutorial CTA Integration","description":"# Purpose

Add a prominent call-to-action for the tutorial system on the brennerbot.org landing page. This is the primary discovery mechanism — users should naturally find the tutorial after understanding what BrennerBot is.

---

# Placement Rationale

**Constraint**: No new navbar item (already crowded with Corpus, Distillations, Method, Operators, Glossary, Sessions)

**Solution**: Prominent section on landing page

**Location**: After the WhatIsThis component, before the feature cards grid

**Rationale**:
1. WhatIsThis explains what BrennerBot is
2. Tutorial CTA offers to teach how to USE it
3. Feature cards provide alternatives for exploration
4. This creates a natural funnel: Learn → Apply → Explore

---

# Design Specification

## Visual Treatment

Use success accent color (green) to stand out from the primary/accent colors used elsewhere. This signals "action available" and creates visual hierarchy.

**Card Design**:
\`\`\`
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  [AcademicCap Icon]                                             │
│                                                                 │
│  Ready to Apply the Method?                                     │
│  Three learning paths from quick start to multi-agent           │
│  orchestration. Apply Brenner's scientific method to your       │
│  own research questions.                                        │
│                                                                 │
│  [~30 min Quick Start] [Agent-Assisted] [Multi-Agent Cockpit]   │
│                                                                 │
│                                          Start Tutorial →       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
\`\`\`

**Styling Details**:
- Border: border-success/30, hover:border-success/50
- Background: gradient from success/5 via success/10 to primary/5
- Icon: Academic cap or graduation cap, size-14, rounded-2xl
- Title: text-xl font-semibold
- Description: text-muted-foreground
- Badges: variant="outline", text-xs
- CTA: text-success font-medium with arrow icon

---

